etomica.data.types

Class DataVector

  • java.lang.Object
    • etomica.data.types.DataVector
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IData, java.io.Serializable

    public class DataVector
extends java.lang.Object
implements IData, java.io.Serializable
    Data object wrapping a single mutable value of type (Space) Vector. Value is final public and can be accessed directly.

    All arithmetic methods throw ClassCastException if given a Data instance that is not of this type.

    See Also:
